# Project III Plant species
### Part of PhD studies of Emil A.S. Andersen

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

This project is for analysis (and data cleaning) of a year-round seasonal project that dealt with plant nitrogen uptake in a subarctic ecosystem located in the north of Sweden.

To better work with and across with other collaborators, I will make certain parts of this project public.
